\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529275\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kmm1665702982567.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kmm1665702982567.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kmm1665702982567.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kmm1665702982567\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Double-Byte Character Set Mnemonics\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">These mnemonics are recognized by the device translation table compiler as double-byte\n    character sets. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kmm1665702982567__section_hh4_xtp_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d274079e51\">Mnemonics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__1\">Mnemonic </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__2\">Synonym </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__3\">Explanation </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">EUC</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__3\">Japanese. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">GB2312</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">GB</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__3\">Simplified Chinese (GB 2312-80). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">KSC5601</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">KSC</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__3\">Korean (KSC 5601). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">SJIS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kmm1665702982567__table_d5642e1_d5643e1_d5644e1__entry__3\">Shift Japanese character set. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kmm1665702982567__p_d64289e1_d64290e1_d64291e1\">The following example defines the Japanese character\n        set:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kmm1665702982567__pre_wgg_15p_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^BEGIN_SET 0\n^027(B ^SELEC\n^SJIS ^CHARSET\n...\n^END_SET\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypn1665702874574.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Developing International Applications</a><p>Uniface supports Unicode and many other character sets, which makes it possible to develop international applications in different languages. It enables you to take locale into account when displaying, sorting, and manipulating data, and to adjust times to the client time zone. It also allows you to configure an application for right-to-left languages.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529275\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529275\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Double-Byte Character Set Mnemonics Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Double-Byte Character Set Mnemonics These mnemonics are recognized by the device translation table compiler as double-byte character sets. Mnemonics Mnemonic Synonym Explanation EUC Japanese. GB2312 GB Simplified Chinese (GB 2312-80). KSC5601 KSC Korean (KSC 5601). SJIS Shift Japanese character set. The following example defines the Japanese character set: ^BEGIN_SET 0 ^027(B ^SELEC ^SJIS ^CHARSET ... ^END_SET Copy Related Links Developing International Applications Uniface supports Unicode and many other character sets, which makes it possible to develop international applications in different languages. It enables you to take locale into account when displaying, sorting, and manipulating data, and to adjust times to the client time zone. It also allows you to configure an application for right-to-left languages. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}